description: The ancient Chinese philosophy of Feng Shui states that not only the things we surround ourselves with, but also the way in which they are positioned have a significant impact on our lives. Everything has an energy. Sometimes these energies attract each other and other times they oppose. This comprehensive ebook provides you with a complete guide to practicing Feng Shui.  Among the many topics included in the book are Methods of Feng Shui, The Five Elements of Feng Shui, The Colors of Feng Shui, Feng Shui For Your Kitchen, Feng Shui in Your Bedroom To Enhance Your Love Life, Using Feng Shui For a Retail Business and many more!  Download this title today and learn the ins and outs of Feng Shui from the Palm of your hand!
